因為如果你用insanity作defence，你就算被判無罪，個原因唔係因為你無犯罪，只係法律上黎講你無咁既能力犯罪，所以你係not guilty by reason of insanity，&rdquo;insanity&rdquo;呢個名就跟住你架啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c706ae5a8ff61254392468a21a19db7ceefb2a8b","tid":1642894,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:51:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29e9d004a1389560219054dda72b60918db2ce06","tid":1642894,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"入小欖仲恐怖"},{"pid":"02e2edfae336b2ad3f22af809306d2fb31f31296","tid":1642894,"uid":184597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:58:57.000Z","msg":"對警察而言，係<br />\n全港公認佢地有精神病<br />\n所以法官都認同"},{"pid":"c87a94a0ecdc0a17b3127ede8c3db65474aebe6a","tid":1642894,"uid":125017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c706ae5a8ff61254392468a21a19db7ceefb2a8b","tid":1642894,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"236b716fd0ad22d0792aedb80569b739f5df1eba","tid":1642894,"uid":296444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b22e029bb8e81bb74a973318aaadc7c739ff18d0","tid":1642894,"uid":310970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:45:21.000Z","msg":"過半港人精神健康不合格：<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/PpRBKo?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2FPpRBKo%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX52CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=6a580930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/PpRBKo?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n休班警忠精神病獲有條件釋放<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191008/60129639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60129639&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX52CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=6507df21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=h